[media] v4l: define own IOCTL ops for SDR FMT

Use own format ops for SDR data:
vidioc_enum_fmt_sdr_cap
vidioc_g_fmt_sdr_cap
vidioc_s_fmt_sdr_cap
vidioc_try_fmt_sdr_cap

